title: Pantera - Gods of Metal Fest DVD
description:
Pantera, the kings of heavy metal, playing the Gods of Metal Fest in Italy on July 6th, 1998. Full menu and artwork. Set list goes :
Walk, New Level, Suicide Note pt.2, War Nerve, Becoming, Sandblasted Skin,
Primal Concrete Sledge, I'm Broken, Number of the Beast, Hostile, This Love, 
Domination/hollow, Cowboys From Hell.
